<HEADLINE> Woman Arrested After Deadly Feud  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   YONKERS, N.Y. (AP) -- A woman who had been feuding with her
neighbor killed the 74-year-old man by repeatedly running him over
with a car after they got into an argument over his use of a leaf
blower, police said.
</P>
<P>
   William Taino was struck in his driveway Wednesday. His neighbor
across the street, Clunie Bernard, 40, was charged with murder.
</P>
