McCoys,'' said Police Commissioner Charles Cola. ''She just
snapped.''
</P>
<P>
   A neighbor, John Williams, said Taino told him that Bernard had
threatened him with a pitchfork while he was using his leaf blower.
</P>
<P>
   ''The mixture of him and the lady together was explosive,''
Williams said. ''They were like two sticks of dynamite waiting to
go off.''
</P>
